# ─── Dependencies ───────────────────────────────
node_modules/

# ─── Environment Variables ──────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production
.env.staging

# ─── Database ───────────────────────────────────
*.sqlite3
*.sqlite

# ─── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ─── Build Output ───────────────────────────────
dist/
build/

# ─── OS Files ───────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─── Editor Files ───────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ─── Vite Specific ──────────────────────────────
frontend/dist/
frontend/.vite/

# ─── Coverage ───────────────────────────────────
coverage/
```

---

## Where to Put It

Since you have both backend and frontend in one project:
```
myProject/
  .gitignore    ← put it HERE at the root
  backend/
  frontend/